<seg id="2082">In & quantaplus; the working area is divided into three areas: global, locally and project-related. this distinction concerns a number of components in & quantaplus;.</seg>
<seg id="2083">Global elements are available for everyone who uses & quantaplus; all that is marked as global is stored in the common folder structure of & quantaplus. this allows the group of administrators to backup different toolbars, actions and patterns in the global tree, which are then available to everyone in a multi-user environment at the system.</seg>
